  "rationale": "Story-before-conversion arc: a centered full-bleed photo hero (reused hero-photo-overlay, the only sanctioned text-on-media) reveals the launch; a left-flush 2x2 cards run renders the four agents as four parallel cells (Swiss grid discipline, no decorative icons); a three-up stat band transfers belief with round brand numbers; a split testimonial anchors the quote left and names the workplace portrait as its counterweight (repairing sec-4's missing counterweight); the reused closing-cta-dark inverse band carries the single ask. Hero uses centered alignment so no counterweight is required, resolving the hero headerContext failure. No footer authored (renderer appends chrome). Accent stays on controls only; headings are sentence-case serif display; no dark bands mid-run."
